New User for Clearing Firm "671" and Exchange "CBOE" !
New User for Clearing Firm "671" and Exchange "CBOE" !

CBSX MKT Order Handling Test Plan: Test Case 1:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS BID PEG CROSS OFFER PEG CROSS is accepted if received prior to or later than the regular trading hours and when Trading Property Enabled Regular Market Time Validation is set to FALSE
Test Case 2:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS BID PEG CROSS OFFER PEG CROSS is accepted if received within the regular trading hours

Test Case 3:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS BID PEG CROSS OFFER PEG CROSS is rejected if received prior to the regular trading hours and when Trading Property Regular Market Time Validation is set to TRUE

Test Case 4:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS BID PEG CROSS OFFER PEG CROSS is rejected if received later than the regular trading hours and when Trading Property Regular Market Time Validation is set to TRUE
Test Case 5:Verify that Market order with contingency BID PEG CROSS is accepted if received prior to or Later than the regular trading hours
Test Scenario A:Matched Cross Order:Trade Immediately
Test Scenario B:Paired Cross Order:Wait and trade
Test Scenario C:Single Cross Order:wait and cancel
Test Case 6:Verify that Market order with contingency OFFER PEG CROSS is accepted if received prior to or Later than the regular trading hours
Test Scenario A:Matched Cross Order:Trade Immediately
Test Scenario B:Paired Cross Order:Wait and trade
Test Scenario C:Single Cross Order:wait and cancel
Test Case 7:Verify that Market order with contingency MIDPOINT CROSS is accepted if received prior to or Later than the regular trading hours
Test Scenario A:Matched Cross Order:Trade Immediately
Test Scenario B:Paired Cross Order:Wait and trade
Test Scenario C:Single Cross Order:wait and cancel
Test Case 8:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS:BID PEG CROSS:OFFER PEG CROSS is accepted during the Regular Trading hours and executed after the Regular Trading hour

Test Case 9:Verify that Market order without contingency MIDPOINT CROSS:BID PEG CROSS:OFFER PEG CROSS is accepted and executed if received during the Regular Trading hours (Closing time is same as opening time)
